    <head><date from-iso="0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042154">京師興唐寺</placeName><persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>傳</head><anchor n="T.50.2061.0760c09"/><p><lb
ed="T" n="0760c10"/><persName key="A009319">釋普寂</persName>，姓<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz7"/>憑<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz7"/>氏，<placeName key="PL000000005197">蒲州河東</placeName>人也。年纔稚弱，率<lb
ed="T" n="0760c11"/>性軒昂，離俗升壇，循于經律。臨文揣義，逈<lb
ed="T" n="0760c12"/>異恒流。初聞<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>在<placeName key="PL000000027023">荊州玉泉寺</placeName>，<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>乃往師<lb
ed="T" n="0760c13"/>事，凡六年。<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>奇<ref type="person" target="#A009319">之</ref>，盡以<ref type="person" target="#A009582">其</ref>道授焉。<date from-iso="0700" key="j19768801977143" to-iso="0701">久視<lb
ed="T" n="0760c14"/>中</date>，<persName key="A002099">則天</persName>召<persName key="A009582">神秀</persName>至<placeName key="PL000000023581">東都</placeName>論道，因薦<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>，乃度<lb
ed="T" n="0760c15"/>為僧。及<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>之卒，天下好釋氏者，咸師事<ref type="person" target="#A009319">之</ref>。<lb
ed="T" n="0760c16"/><persName key="A002100">中宗</persName>聞<persName key="A009582">秀</persName>高年，特下制令<persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>代<ref type="person" target="#A009582">本師</ref><ptr type="glossary" target="#g190"/>統<lb
ed="T" n="0760c17"/>其法眾。<date from-iso="0735-02-02" key="j19895451989927" to-iso="0736-02-19">開元二十三年</date>，勅<persName key="A009319">普寂</persName>於<ref type="place" target="#PL000000042189 #PL000000023581">都城</ref>居<lb
ed="T" n="0760c18"/>止。時王公大人競來<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz8"/>禮<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz8"/>謁，<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>嚴重少言，來者<lb
ed="T" n="0760c19"/>難見其和悅之容，遠近尤以此重<ref type="person" target="#A009319">之</ref>。<date from-iso="0739-02-17" key="j19910211991374" to-iso="0740-02-05">二十七<lb
ed="T" n="0760c20"/>年</date>，終于<placeName key="PL000000042154">上都興唐寺</placeName>。年八十九。時都城士庶<lb
ed="T" n="0760c21"/>謁者皆制弟<anchor xml:id="beg0760sgsz9"/>子<anchor xml:id="end0760sgsz9"/>之服。有制賜諡曰<persName key="A009319">大慧禪<lb
ed="T" n="0760c22"/>師</persName>。及葬，河南尹<persName key="A009351">裴寬</persName>及其妻子，並縗麻列于<lb
ed="T" n="0760c23"/>門徒之次。傾城哭送，閭里為之空焉。<ref type="person" target="#A009351">裴尹</ref><lb
ed="T" n="0760c24"/>之重<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>，職有由矣。<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>之闡化，神異頗多，<persName key="A009351">裴</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0760c25"/>皆目擊，又得心印，歸向越深。時多譏誚，<persName key="A009351">裴</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0760c26"/>日夕造謁，執弟子禮曾無差脫。一日詣<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0760c27"/><persName key="A009319">寂</persName>懸知弟子<persName key="A000008">一行</persName>之亡。及<persName key="A009319">寂</persName>之終滅，<persName key="A009351">裴</persName>之<lb
ed="T" n="0760c28"/>悲慟若喪所親，縗絰徒步出城，妻子同爾，<lb
ed="T" n="0760c29"/>搢紳之譏生於是矣。</p><pb ed="T" n="0761a" xml:id="T50.2061.0761a"/>
    <p><lb
ed="T" n="0761a01"/>系曰：人之情也有愛惡焉，愛之者不見可<lb
ed="T" n="0761a02"/>惡，惡之者不見可愛矣。夫萬物紛綸，任其<lb
ed="T" n="0761a03"/>愛惡，折中之道，可愛而不可惡。愛之者君<lb
ed="T" n="0761a04"/>子也，惡之者小人也，愛之不以道，則君子<lb
ed="T" n="0761a05"/>之病矣。<ref type="person" target="#A009351">裴尹</ref>冠裳在御，職事在躬，不避密<lb
ed="T" n="0761a06"/>行，顯掇時謗，宜哉。譬諸僧耽俗務，胡不<lb
ed="T" n="0761a07"/>捨袈裟而衣逢掖乎？若實得道，後終期脫<lb
ed="T" n="0761a08"/>屣，有何不可<anchor xml:id="beg0761001"/>耶<anchor xml:id="end0761001"/>？寬不抽簪，何悖禮於丘<lb
ed="T" n="0761a09"/>之門歟？寬若行方外之道，復何誅焉。達人<lb
ed="T" n="0761a10"/>大觀，物無不可矣。</p>
